############
Installation
############

This code is open-source. See :doc:`/about/license` for details.

If you want to contribute to the code, you should go to
:doc:`/contribute/index` documentation.

Install the package with your favorite Python installer. As an example, with
pip:

.. code-block:: sh

   # Not released yet on PyPI, so use the source...
   pip install https://github.com/benoitbryon/xal.git#egg=xal

See :doc:`api/index` for a detailed usage documentation.
